{"id": "ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 159, "displayName": {"text": "Neighbors & Friends Cafe", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aWFJsbFBWWGx4V21aUVNGaHNWWEpMU1RWNmVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I found them from an IG food review, like many others. So when I went they were out of several menu items because it was such a great review. They ended up making me a build your own breakfast sandwich and it was delicious! I had turkey, eggs and cheese on sourdough bread. That bread was magnificent, so perfect! One of the best sandwiches ever! I went back the following weekend and got the same sandwich but on a flaky, buttery, delicious croissant! Which was equally great! I'm not really down with community seating, which is why I gave atmosphere a 3, but the staff is wonderful, great customer service and genuinely seem happy to work there. My sandwich was a little pricey compared to what I'm used to paying. It was almost $17, I usually pay between $10 and $13.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I found them from an IG food review, like many others. So when I went they were out of several menu items because it was such a great review. They ended up making me a build your own breakfast sandwich and it was delicious! I had turkey, eggs and cheese on sourdough bread. That bread was magnificent, so perfect! One of the best sandwiches ever! I went back the following weekend and got the same sandwich but on a flaky, buttery, delicious croissant! Which was equally great! I'm not really down with community seating, which is why I gave atmosphere a 3, but the staff is wonderful, great customer service and genuinely seem happy to work there. My sandwich was a little pricey compared to what I'm used to paying. It was almost $17, I usually pay between $10 and $13.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Eddie Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107490353722037808181/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaq97bs-3-ZN-WppHJOS8V0NXq8DILc1Gt86TCcjSdCb_Mpj0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-25T15:27:00.957141466Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aWFJsbFBWWGx4V21aUVNGaHNWWEpMU1RWNmVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aWFJsbFBWWGx4V21aUVNGaHNWWEpMU1RWNmVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c300646ac2bf:0x9e86be62b8685135"}, {"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxWGRVNTRNVGxQTjNveE4zQnRXV1poUlc1Tk5WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "While this place is known for their beautiful charcuterie boxes, they're also a solid spot for brunch as well. My wife and I visited right at their opening hours on a weekend and it was such a good experience.\n\nIt's more of a order then sit down type spot. They have some tables but not too many. Parking here in Pasadena is as usual, mainly just parking in paid garages, metered street parking.\n\nMy wife and I ordered the Deviled egg stuffed croissant and the Roasted Chick Sandwich to share and the orders came out pretty quickly. There's not much service other than that, staff is friendly which is great to see at least.\n\nThe croissant is very tasty. However, it's pretty messy to eat as you can't really eat it neatly. The croissant itself is pretty standard, not too tough and the egg is soft which is the best part. 8/10, recommend\n\nThe Roasted Chick Sandwich on the other hand is a great sandwich. I'd never had mango jam in a sandwich like this so this is a first experience. It's a bit....interesting? It's savory yet a bit sweet so if you're a fan of that type of taste, then I highly recommend this. It's tasty regardless. The chicken mixes surprisingly well with the mango which is nice. 8/10, recommend\n\nOverall, a decent brunch spot, saw plenty signs for their charcuterie boards/boxes so I'm definitely interested in returning to check those out. I'd say that the menu items are a bit expensive for brunch, but it's certainly worth a try as one of the popular places in Pasadena.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "While this place is known for their beautiful charcuterie boxes, they're also a solid spot for brunch as well. My wife and I visited right at their opening hours on a weekend and it was such a good experience.\n\nIt's more of a order then sit down type spot. They have some tables but not too many. Parking here in Pasadena is as usual, mainly just parking in paid garages, metered street parking.\n\nMy wife and I ordered the Deviled egg stuffed croissant and the Roasted Chick Sandwich to share and the orders came out pretty quickly. There's not much service other than that, staff is friendly which is great to see at least.\n\nThe croissant is very tasty. However, it's pretty messy to eat as you can't really eat it neatly. The croissant itself is pretty standard, not too tough and the egg is soft which is the best part. 8/10, recommend\n\nThe Roasted Chick Sandwich on the other hand is a great sandwich. I'd never had mango jam in a sandwich like this so this is a first experience. It's a bit....interesting? It's savory yet a bit sweet so if you're a fan of that type of taste, then I highly recommend this. It's tasty regardless. The chicken mixes surprisingly well with the mango which is nice. 8/10, recommend\n\nOverall, a decent brunch spot, saw plenty signs for their charcuterie boards/boxes so I'm definitely interested in returning to check those out. I'd say that the menu items are a bit expensive for brunch, but it's certainly worth a try as one of the popular places in Pasadena.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kevin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102328750167324980680/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU8uByaiuI6kB15QC2QrPSwXHiBWTQ5Heq75Wu9TwRBLfonwA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-10T14:23:29.081098284Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxWGRVNTRNVGxQTjNveE4zQnRXV1poUlc1Tk5WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxWGRVNTRNVGxQTjNveE4zQnRXV1poUlc1Tk5WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c300646ac2bf:0x9e86be62b8685135"}, {"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GR1dVZFpOMmsxWW04MVEzbE5hSEJsYUVKWFZIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We were visiting from New York and were drawn to this cafe because of their mission to not only serve their own food, but the baked goods of other local  producers.\n\nSimply put, these were the two best sandwiches we’ve ever eaten. The figgy piggy is beyond exceptional. Every man, woman, person, and child should try this sandwich.\n\nThe Roasted Chick sandwich was expertly balanced, with the mango lemon jam serving as a perfect complement to the chicken and arugula, in between a soft milk bun.\n\nEvery bite was so good we had to stop talking to enjoy every bite.\n\nThe coffee here is also delicious.\n\nMust try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We were visiting from New York and were drawn to this cafe because of their mission to not only serve their own food, but the baked goods of other local  producers.\n\nSimply put, these were the two best sandwiches we’ve ever eaten. The figgy piggy is beyond exceptional. Every man, woman, person, and child should try this sandwich.\n\nThe Roasted Chick sandwich was expertly balanced, with the mango lemon jam serving as a perfect complement to the chicken and arugula, in between a soft milk bun.\n\nEvery bite was so good we had to stop talking to enjoy every bite.\n\nThe coffee here is also delicious.\n\nMust try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Zachary Altman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106731746941830234305/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKr0PzvjdG995yKvbQMJp6ejT3HM9MAiNrrzMOjC-jq23lYNw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-07T12:09:26.195347250Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GR1dVZFpOMmsxWW04MVEzbE5hSEJsYUVKWFZIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GR1dVZFpOMmsxWW04MVEzbE5hSEJsYUVKWFZIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c300646ac2bf:0x9e86be62b8685135"}, {"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST2JHTmtlRkZIZFVablVXSklVa0pDTkhscGVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We had such a lovely time at our favorite Pasadena cafe! Our group enjoyed the ricotta croissant, grump sandwich, and cotton candy lemonade. What a lovely way to spend a Sunday in Old Town!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We had such a lovely time at our favorite Pasadena cafe! Our group enjoyed the ricotta croissant, grump sandwich, and cotton candy lemonade. What a lovely way to spend a Sunday in Old Town!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Stella Pavao", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100182897172849363696/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-OTkMSxLrUPUaFzGw7krZbBDApCWlsrCFSz2RrlZEbteJM1KE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T18:04:17.936494105Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST2JHTmtlRkZIZFVablVXSklVa0pDTkhscGVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ST2JHTmtlRkZIZFVablVXSklVa0pDTkhscGVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c300646ac2bf:0x9e86be62b8685135"}, {"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCSGNXeFJWMnRJTFhGUU4wbHFYMnhITmkwMWNHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "As soon as you walk in you feel like you’re in your “neighborhood”\n\nAll the staff immediately turns to greet and welcome you.\n\nMenu is large enough to satisfy anyone’s taste.\n\nSeating area is very comfy and food/coffee are great.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "As soon as you walk in you feel like you’re in your “neighborhood”\n\nAll the staff immediately turns to greet and welcome you.\n\nMenu is large enough to satisfy anyone’s taste.\n\nSeating area is very comfy and food/coffee are great.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Juan Camilo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114576589694717281149/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIunV-Q_FvJl5uG7sUqT0evg42bOVZBYWr90ynmGmZRSBT_EA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T19:23:50.352117567Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCSGNXeFJWMnRJTFhGUU4wbHFYMnhITmkwMWNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCSGNXeFJWMnRJTFhGUU4wbHFYMnhITmkwMWNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c300646ac2bf:0x9e86be62b8685135"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJv8JqZADDwoARNVFouGK-hp4/photos/AWCwydg3XWujpicfyDNaQjZyLEXdySBNiArZJbyzon5I45c8cqvqkNQ3GZ0Yjg6U0KirZMhrAwVpdEJqug-2hHo3kDZT53KA8b4FpZhvcbIqmTrA2KfRORsYXJvsmQOrp08CqHuq5oTtdNrscviGB9hlXAXED65k_QEJSdIMZB80m4NtaZt20OyOw91aFHrO-horwgOW-_yQ-IPj4kc5H9rslY1dhp4iBr4le-7mGuwTOk9sgmQWf7LqvYOrN9YPL_XNVxqPacBnSWbP814PFEer5hFTStfjYZ69d-UAOPYBXMoCD1XWCJb3vE1VjAa8yg6mbXQXllZsZbU14f_s